Package ca.projectTOMi.tomi.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    A model class that contains information about accounts in the TOMi system.
    Client
    A model class for storing information related to the Client.
    Expense
    An Expense is anything other than a user's billable hours that is being charged towards a Project's budget.
    Project
    A Project represents a project that either needs to be completed, or has been completed (dependent on it's active status.) Projects are worked on by specific Account lead by a project manager.
    Task
    A task represents a deliverable for the client.
    Team
    A Team represents a group of Accounts whom work under the same team lead.
    Timesheet
    class representing a single timesheet for a user for a specific week.
    UnitType  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Status
    represents the submission status of a timesheet or entry
